title: Keiko Matsui The Jazz Channel Presents BET on Jazz (2000)
description: Keyboardist and composer Keiko Matsui performs a blend of jazz and New Age instrumental compositions before a live audience for the "BET on Jazz" program in Washington, D.C. Matsui and her band offer their renditions of "Night Hawks&#039; Dream," "Kappa," "Night Waltz," "Forever, Forever" and "Light Above the Trees." Matsui also brings out her record-producer husband to play the shakuhachi (a Japanese bamboo flute) for the final three numbers.
